# 🫀 InteractiveHeartBeat

An interactive 3D heartbeat animation built using **Three.js** and **Vite**.  
This project simulates the rhythmic pulsing of a human heart — ideal for educational demos or portfolio projects.

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

🚀 [Check it out here](https://your-live-link-goes-here.com)  
*(Replace this with your Netlify/Vercel/GitHub Pages link)*

---

## Features

- 💓 Real-time heartbeat animation in 3D
- 🧠 Clean, modular code using ES6+
- ⚡️ Super fast dev environment with Vite
- 🔁 Responsive and looped pulse effect
- 🎨 Perfect for UI demos or WebGL experiments

---

## Tech Stack

| Tech        | Description                                  |
|-------------|----------------------------------------------|
| [Three.js]| 3D rendering engine for creating the heartbeat |
| [Vite]| Fast dev server and build tool |
| JavaScript | Modern JavaScript for animation logic |
| HTML5 & CSS3 | Basic layout and styling |

---

## Getting Started

To run this project locally:

```bash
# 1. Clone the repo
git clone git@github.com:TanaNazarevych/InteractiveHeartBeat.git
cd InteractiveHeartBeat

# 2. Install dependencies
npm install

# 3. Start the development server
npm run dev
